  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON:  The proposed retention of the internally illuminated poster panel by reason of its excessive design, scale, method of illumination and prominent location is considered to create a visually dominant and harmful feature to the surrounding area along Camden Road. The development therefore fails to respect its local context and pattern of development while having a significant detrimental impact on the character and appearance of the Hillmarton Conservation Area. The proposed retention of the advertisement panel is therefore considered to be contrary to polices D1, D4, D24, Env 11 of Islington’s Unitary Development Plan 2002, Islington’s Urban design guidance 2006, Hillmarton conservation guidance note and PPS 17."
